  <h2> There are many popular celebrities in the Indian world, and most are mainly popularly known as being actors of Bollywood. In Bollywood, there isn't as much action as there is romance and drama. These types of flims are usually complicated, but one thing they all have in common: A love story. Some famous actors are Shah Rukh Khan, on the left, and Kareena Kapoor, on the right. <h2>
  <a href="https://www.patrika.com/bollywood-news/shah-rukh-khan-might-play-a-cop-in-madhur-bhandarkar-upcoming-film-4083628/"><img align="left"src= "shah-rukh-khan.jpg" width="500" height="300"></a>
