  <h2>One of the oldest and most famous Indian Actors is Amitabh Bachchan, and he is probably the most renown actors of all time as well. He is not only just an actor, he is also a game show host for the most famous game show in India, 'Kaun Bannega Karorepati?', which means, 'Who will be the Millionaire?'. Mr. Bachchan has also donated a lot of money to charity over the years and is very religious.</h2>
